import { DefaultTheme } from 'react-native-paper';

export const theme = {
  ...DefaultTheme,
  colors: {
    text: '#000000',
    primary: '#390A41',
    secondary: '#414757',
    bgColor: '#F7E9FA',
    error: '#f13a59',
  },
  siteColor: {
    colo090909: '#090909',
    color7C7C7C: '#7C7C7C',
    color222222: '#222222',
    colorCC933B: '#CC933B',
    colorFFFFFF: '#FFFFFF',
    colorC68625: '#C68625',
    color666666: '#666666',
    color0D0D0D: '#0D0D0D',
    color272727: '#272727',
    color999999: '#999999',
    color777777: '#777777',
    color333333: '#333333',
    color050505: '#050505',
    color444444: '#444444',
    colorEEEEEE: '#EEEEEE',
    color111111: '#111111',
    colorF5F5F5: '#F5F5F5',
    colorDDDDDD: '#DDDDDD',
    colorC4C4C4: '#C4C4C4',
    colorFFD640: '#FFD640',
    color27272A: '#27272A',
    colorE3E3E3: '#E3E3E3',
    color9e9da4: '#9e9da4',
    color444550: '#444550',
    colora8a6af: '#a8a6af',
    colorede9f1: '#ede9f1',
    color686a78: '#686a78',
  },
  fontsT: {
    fontS8: 10,
    fontS9: 11,
    fontS10: 12,
    fontS11: 13,
    fontS12: 14,
    fontS13: 15,
    fontS14: 16,
    fontS15: 17,
    fontS16: 18,

  },
  fontsM: {
    fontS8: 8,
    fontS9: 9,
    fontS10: 10,
    fontS11: 11,
    fontS12: 12,
    fontS13: 13,
    fontS14: 14,
    fontS15: 15,
    fontS16: 16,

  },
  lineHeightT: {
    lineH10: 12,
    lineH11: 13,
    lineH12: 14,
    lineH14: 16,
    lineH15: 17,
    lineH16: 18,
    lineH18: 20,
  },
  lineHeightM: {
    lineH10: 10,
    lineH11: 11,
    lineH12: 12,
    lineH14: 14,
    lineH15: 15,
    lineH16: 16,
    lineH18: 18,

}
